description.en: Orclands Metaverse is a NFT based Play 2 Earn game deployed on the Binance Smart Chain. Game play consists of NFT Battles, NFT Farming for rewards and NFT Mining for treasures. There is also an Orc Markets where NFT's can be swapped or rented for game play.
